OL,3,CVietnam War helmet found in charity
OL,4,Cshop to be returned to US family
OL,6,FAn amateur historian from who bought a
OL,7,FWar helmet has tracked down the
OL,8,FAmerican soldier who wore it and is
OL,9,Fplanning to return it to his family.
OL,11,FMilitary enthusiast Hugo Booth
OL,12,Facquired the M1 helmet from an auction
OL,13,Fon the island after it was found in a
OL,14,Fcharity shop.
OL,16,FHe noticed that the name 'Rupp' was
OL,17,Fwritten on the Kevlar insert, as well
OL,18,Fas the peace sign and the words 'Vote
OL,19,F'.
