OL,6,FHugo linked the helmet to Private
OL,7,FFirst Class Jeffrey Rupp of the 101st
OL,8,FAirbourne Division in the US Army.
OL,10,FA 1969 telegram explained that Jeffrey
OL,11,Fwas injured by shrapnel from a booby
OL,12,Ftrap near the Cambodian border.
OL,14,FHugo understands that the 20-year-old
OL,15,Fsoldier died of his wounds on a
OL,16,Fhospital ship on 17 January 1969.
