OL,6,FHugo and his father Tony Booth
OL,7,Feventually found David Rupp, Jeffery's
OL,8,Fnephew, through an online appeal and
OL,9,Fare planning to visit America to
OL,10,Fdeliver the helmet personally to
OL,11,FWisconsin.
OL,13,FDavid says: "I'm not sure how my mum,
OL,14,Fmy aunt and my uncles are going to
OL,15,Fhandle that ... they didn't get to see
OL,16,Fthe body so this is going to be the
OL,17,Fclosest thing, it probably will be
OL,18,Fvery emotional.
