OL,6,F"The odds of this happening are
OL,7,Fabsolutely incredible and I'm just
OL,8,Fglad it happened to us."
OL,10,FTony adds: "It seems to have captured
OL,11,Fthe hearts of the American people.
OL,13,F"Lots of Vietnam veterans have put
OL,14,Fcomments on, praising Hugo for what
OL,15,Fhe's trying to do and I'll support him
OL,16,Fall I can for that.
