OL,6,F"Private Rupp's sister couldn't
OL,7,Fbelieve it and she very much wants the
OL,8,Fhelmet back in her possession as a
OL,9,Fmemento of her brother, what he
OL,10,Fachieved and what he suffered."
OL,12,FHugo is still researching how
OL,13,FJeffrey's helmet made it thousands of
OL,14,Fmiles to Guernsey.
OL,16,FHe explains: "You start to get to know
OL,17,Fthe person who owned the helmet and it
OL,18,Fbecomes a lot more personal.
