OL,6,F"It's nice to give back a piece of him
OL,7,Fas a way to be remembered by his
OL,8,Ffamily."
OL,10,FPart of the helmet's journey saw it
OL,11,Fbeing used as a film prop and involved
OL,12,FHollywood star Oliver Reed.
OL,14,FIt is understood that he gave the
OL,15,Fpiece of military history to a friend
OL,16,Fin Guernsey before it made its way to
OL,17,Fthe charity shop.
OL,19,FTony and Hugo aim to travel over to
OL,20,FAmerica with the helmet this summer.
